---
import pfLogo from '../assets/pflogo.png';
import aboutImage from '../assets/retail.jpg';
---
<div class="overflow-hidden bg-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="lg:pr-8 lg:pt-4">
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-400" id="about">Who we are</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Pixelfoorge Ltd is a UK-based creative agency specializing in the development and optimization of content for LED video walls, interactive displays, and immersive environments.
 
.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">We also support clients with business content strategy, B2B media presentation, and cross-platform digital campaigns.</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300"><strong>Our services </strong>include video editing, animation loop creation, system configuration (Novastar, Colorlight), remote playback management, and technical support for live displays.</p>

          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">Whether you're launching a new product, organizing an event, or building brand awareness, Pixelfoorg delivers visuals that speak volumes.</p>
  
        </div>
      </div>
      <img src={aboutImage.src} alt="Product screenshot" class="w-[48rem] max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-white/10 sm:w-[57rem] md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0" width="2432" height="1442">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer class="bg-gray-900" aria-labelledby="footer-heading">
  <h2 id="footer-heading" class="sr-only">Footer</h2>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 lg:px-8 lg:py-32">
    <div class="xl:grid xl:grid-cols-3 xl:gap-8">
      <img class="h-24" src={pfLogo.src} alt="Pixelfoorge Logo" />
      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 xl:col-span-2 xl:mt-0">
        <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white">Services</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-4">
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Video Editing</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Animation Loop Creation</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">System Configuration</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Remote Playback</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10 md:mt-0">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white">Solutions</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-4">
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Content Development</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Content Strategy</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">B2B Media Presentation</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Cross Platform Digital Campaings</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white">Company</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-4">
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">71-75 Shelton Street, Covent Garden, London, WC2H 9JQ</a>
              </li>
              
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10 md:mt-0">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white">Legal</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="mt-6 space-y-4">
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Privacy</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#" class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 hover:text-white">Terms</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
